{"tid":826502,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"竟然俾我見到鄰國網民咁樣評價香港人","createTime":"2018-09-18T09:35:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T10:52:12.000Z","uid":73366,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"416f30b082ef8cb1d77dce8550e08191b2b3d352","tid":826502,"uid":73366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/173135_7e99bbcc4d8676af907f96504fbf27f5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F173135_7e99bbcc4d8676af907f96504fbf27f5.png&h=4e3c720a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/173142_a08608a0161391fabcb9ccaa4fd838d7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F173142_a08608a0161391fabcb9ccaa4fd838d7.png&h=99fd45f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n工作需要，成日要mon住微博鄰國人啲post，咁理性咁讚香港人真係少見。風災後秩序都好到咁，又有好多司機肯義載，講公民質素其實真係唔輸日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdab58069a8c5adf915732a687a4729bee4b4085","tid":826502,"uid":208726,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:39:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d37c4adacec8f39c201e5c6016375b1da02d60f1","tid":826502,"uid":27416,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:40:14.000Z","msg":"崇日撚哭了"},{"pid":"1903cb6d96c0ae6076b7b2d3dc86f524dd2e6442","tid":826502,"uid":73356,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"d37c4adacec8f39c201e5c6016375b1da02d60f1","tid":826502,"uid":27416,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:40:14.000Z","msg":"崇日撚哭了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:44:06.000Z","msg":"係都踩港撚哭先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac4a3401f8284f603e390554cd261260f5a05489","tid":826502,"uid":32722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T09:45: